todoList.title: Dust Fans
todoList.notes: Use blade cleaner to catch all the dust. Wear PPE to protect face and nose.

todoList.title: Organize Garage
todoList.notes: Use plastic bins and label each one! They can stack on shelf or in the attic.

todoList.title: Paint Deck
todoList.notes: Use Sherman Williams Deck Wash to prep and Charwood color Top Deck Stain.

todoList.title: Detail SUV
todoList.notes: Use Turtlewax, and don't forget to to the rims. Also, don'r forget to vacuum the trunk.

todoList.title: Organize Plants
todoList.notes: Re-pot and throw away any dead plants! Also, put empty pots into shed.

todoList.title: Paint Bathroom
todoList.notes: Make sure to clean the walls first and tape off the corners and lay down plastic.

todoList.title: Sweep Garage
todoList.notes: Make sure to sweep all corners! Use the leaf blower when done.

todoList.title: Clean out Refrigerator
todoList.notes: Throw away all old food. Take out all shelves and wash thoroughly. Use plastic bins from Amazon.

todoList.title: Clean out front and backyard
todoList.notes: Make sure to organize all dog toys. Also rake any leaves and fallen branches.
